{
  "stem": "4345.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember saying this to him, as young as I was, I remember the songs that we sang in Polish about Israel-- in Polish about Palestine, about [INAUDIBLE] about-- I knew about the Balfour Declaration.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew all these things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I use to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Books were available.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Polish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would read about-- on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would read on-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the-- the [INAUDIBLE] in is the-- You know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also a beautiful book.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got this from my teacher, my Hebrew teacher, as a token of appreciation for my beautiful Hebrew that I spoke.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I spoke fluent Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did and then, then during the Nazi years, the beatings, and the-- and the-- the troubles that we suffered-- the pain and the suffering-- it zapped us of everything, including the-- We were afraid to use anything, you know, Jewish, although they knew that we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were told-- it's-- it's amazing how I remember these-- these pictures in silhouette on the walls.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where you see a skull-- like a skeleton-- and then you would hear, shh [GERMAN], be quiet, because the [INAUDIBLE] is listening-- your enemy is listening.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they meant us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They meant us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They meant the Jews-- that we should not talk, because the enemy is listening in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was during the-- when the Nazis came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we were afraid to talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were times we were afraid to laugh and to cry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, it was-- it was-- it was bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I went to Bais Yaakov.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was busy with school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was only about eight, nine years old. 10-- even 10, I was still a young child.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
